1
00:00:48,460 --> 00:00:52,620
=Endless Love=

2
00:00:52,660 --> 00:00:55,580
=Episode 16=

3
00:01:09,319 --> 00:01:10,120
Since you're here,

4
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:11,319
why not take a seat and share a drink?

5
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:16,280
I heard
you're a regular at the brothels.

6
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:18,519
Says who?

7
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:19,920
You?

8
00:01:20,239 --> 00:01:21,120
Shameless!

9
00:01:22,879 --> 00:01:24,159
We just met today.

10
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:27,040
How do you know

11
00:01:27,319 --> 00:01:28,239
where I've been?

12
00:01:28,439 --> 00:01:29,640
Were you following me?

13
00:01:30,120 --> 00:01:32,040
I have no time for your sneaky games.

14
00:01:32,519 --> 00:01:33,599
Why did you go to a brothel?

15
00:01:34,040 --> 00:01:36,000
And why did you stage that kidnapping?

16
00:01:36,879 --> 00:01:38,640
Are you plotting
against Her Highness again?

17
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:43,400
I never set up any scheme.

18
00:01:43,879 --> 00:01:45,159
I've never been to a brothel.

19
00:01:45,359 --> 00:01:46,480
And I didn't save the Princess.

20
00:01:47,439 --> 00:01:48,319
The one who saved her

21
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:51,120
must be lying awake
in the palace right now.

22
00:01:53,040 --> 00:01:53,879
It's your...

23
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,719
I see.

24
00:01:57,599 --> 00:01:59,760
Ling Xiao, that heartless wretch,

25
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:02,120
has learned to use your name
as a disguise.

26
00:02:03,599 --> 00:02:04,640
I see you two

27
00:02:05,319 --> 00:02:07,359
have always been in cahoots.

28
00:02:07,519 --> 00:02:08,360
You are birds of a feather.

29
00:02:12,039 --> 00:02:12,680
Ke'er,

30
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:14,400
what happened before

31
00:02:15,599 --> 00:02:16,520
was beyond our control.

32
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:18,159
But now,

33
00:02:18,759 --> 00:02:19,759
the Princess and Ling Xiao

34
00:02:19,759 --> 00:02:21,000
have both moved on

35
00:02:22,479 --> 00:02:24,080
and are living so carefree.

36
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:26,039
Why can't we

37
00:02:27,039 --> 00:02:28,000
be the same?

38
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:32,120
All this time,

39
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:34,479
we've been through
life and death together.

40
00:02:34,879 --> 00:02:35,879
I've done a lot of thinking.

41
00:02:37,759 --> 00:02:38,759
In my heart,

42
00:02:41,199 --> 00:02:42,439
I still can't let you go.

43
00:02:47,159 --> 00:02:47,879
Mo Shuo,

44
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,439
I did trust you once.

45
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:54,080
We had days of joy and happiness.

46
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:56,599
I've even thought about

47
00:02:58,120 --> 00:03:00,120
if I weren't the general of Xiling

48
00:03:01,439 --> 00:03:02,960
or the Princess's confidant,

49
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:06,759
what would become of us?

50
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,520
But the facts cannot be changed.

51
00:03:11,719 --> 00:03:13,919
The hatred between Xiling and Dongqing

52
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:15,759
will never be forgotten.

53
00:03:17,639 --> 00:03:19,800
The love and hate
between the Princess and Ling Xiao

54
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:23,520
are not something
we can just turn a blind eye to

55
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:26,639
and easily overcome.

56
00:03:34,879 --> 00:03:35,719
Xia Ke'er.

57
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:38,120
I come from
the royal family of Dongqing.

58
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:41,199
Once, I believed my bloodline,

59
00:03:41,439 --> 00:03:42,800
my destiny, and my burdens

60
00:03:42,919 --> 00:03:44,000
were all destined,

61
00:03:44,759 --> 00:03:45,800
and I could never change them.

62
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,800
But ever since I met you,

63
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:54,159
I've realized

64
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:58,520
that in my life,

65
00:03:59,759 --> 00:04:00,919
there are surprises

66
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:03,080
and possibilities.

67
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,520
Enough.

68
00:04:07,919 --> 00:04:08,800
Say more,

69
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:11,759
and I might start believing you.

70
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:15,159
You are nothing but an enemy prince

71
00:04:15,439 --> 00:04:17,040
planted beside me

72
00:04:17,399 --> 00:04:19,240
to scheme and spy.

73
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:21,160
And I...

74
00:04:22,519 --> 00:04:25,199
I am merely a piece you use and control.

75
00:04:26,879 --> 00:04:28,920
Isn't love between us

76
00:04:32,399 --> 00:04:33,879
too absurd?

77
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:37,839
What do I have to do

78
00:04:37,839 --> 00:04:39,000
for you to trust me?

79
00:04:56,879 --> 00:04:57,639
What do you want?

80
00:04:57,879 --> 00:04:59,120
The blood feud

81
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:01,720
between Dongqing and Xiling
will never be settled,

82
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:06,079
and what lies between us
will never be clear.

83
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:09,480
So let me take the Oblivion Herb

84
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:12,439
and forget it all alone.

85
00:05:13,519 --> 00:05:14,759
It would be better than this.

86
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:16,879
What are you doing?

87
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:19,040
Spit it out!

88
00:05:19,199 --> 00:05:20,040
Spit it out now!

89
00:05:21,759 --> 00:05:22,319
Mo Shuo,

90
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:23,360
are you alright?

91
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:24,879
Do you remember me?

92
00:05:25,079 --> 00:05:26,079
Say something!

93
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:35,639
Ke'er,

94
00:05:37,399 --> 00:05:38,879
you do care about me.

95
00:05:40,639 --> 00:05:41,800
You fooled me again!

96
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:45,439
You are a master of schemes.

97
00:05:49,319 --> 00:05:51,639
Whether a noble man or a cunning one,

98
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:54,279
as long as I can stay by your side,

99
00:05:55,519 --> 00:05:57,279
I don't care about being a gentleman

100
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,199
or a villain.

101
00:05:59,959 --> 00:06:00,839
I'm willing to give you

102
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:03,319
everything I have.

103
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:35,120
Mo Shuo,

104
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:37,319
this is what you owe me.

105
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:39,319
Until the day you die,

106
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:41,360
you belong to no one but me.

107
00:06:44,959 --> 00:06:45,560
As you command.

108
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:47,360
Whatever you say

109
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:51,160
are words I will follow.

110
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:58,040
Liu Rushi?

111
00:07:00,759 --> 00:07:01,600
Why is her face,

112
00:07:02,079 --> 00:07:02,879
her name,

113
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:04,759
even her scent

114
00:07:05,759 --> 00:07:06,759
so familiar to me?

115
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:15,120
Your Majesty.

116
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:16,519
Let me check.

117
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:17,720
What's wrong with you now?

118
00:07:18,959 --> 00:07:20,839
Is it because of the person
from yesterday?

119
00:07:21,319 --> 00:07:22,120
How do you know?

120
00:07:22,439 --> 00:07:23,439
Do you know that lady?

121
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:26,079
No, I don't.

122
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,120
As of today,

123
00:07:29,319 --> 00:07:31,120
you will not leave this palace,

124
00:07:31,399 --> 00:07:33,759
and you will not use my identity
to cause any trouble.

125
00:07:34,399 --> 00:07:36,120
Then why do you call me "Your Majesty"?

126
00:07:36,519 --> 00:07:37,639
Then how did you find out

127
00:07:37,839 --> 00:07:39,000
that I used your identity?

128
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:41,560
Do you think Sheng and the other guards

129
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:42,519
just sit around doing nothing?

130
00:07:45,759 --> 00:07:47,079
All you do is confine me.

131
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:49,079
I have no freedom at all!

132
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:51,199
If this continues,
I'll lose my mind more,

133
00:07:51,279 --> 00:07:52,120
and my health will get worse!

134
00:07:52,279 --> 00:07:52,839
Your Majesty.

135
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:54,720
Once you've recovered,

136
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,160
you may come and go as you please.

137
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:57,600
Really?

138
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:00,319
That's my brother!

139
00:08:02,399 --> 00:08:03,639
I'll take the pill!

140
00:08:05,879 --> 00:08:06,839
(But I wonder,)

141
00:08:07,519 --> 00:08:08,759
(to you, is Mu Ruyi)

142
00:08:09,439 --> 00:08:10,439
(a curse)

143
00:08:10,959 --> 00:08:11,920
(or a cure?)

144
00:08:19,279 --> 00:08:20,920
Where did she go?

145
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:22,600
She didn't come back all night!

146
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:35,679
Who is this?

147
00:08:41,039 --> 00:08:42,440
What's with the sneaking around?

148
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,759
I'm not.

149
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:45,360
Come clean now!

150
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:50,679
I went to right a wrong for you.

151
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:52,879
I found the slave traders
and turned them in.

152
00:08:54,759 --> 00:08:56,080
To avenge you!

153
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:59,879
I never even described them

154
00:09:00,159 --> 00:09:01,360
or told you the place,

155
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:02,919
how did you know?

156
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:04,559
And how did you find them?

157
00:09:06,519 --> 00:09:07,399
Good point.

158
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:08,919
How about

159
00:09:10,159 --> 00:09:11,200
you tell me now?

160
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:20,320
Don't try to fool me.

161
00:09:20,759 --> 00:09:23,519
A young lady who stayed out all night,

162
00:09:23,919 --> 00:09:26,279
wearing someone else's scent.

163
00:09:27,679 --> 00:09:30,840
You must have been sneaking off
to meet someone,

164
00:09:31,399 --> 00:09:32,600
unable to control yourself,

165
00:09:32,759 --> 00:09:33,639
lost in passion,

166
00:09:33,799 --> 00:09:34,799
and staying all night.

167
00:09:35,159 --> 00:09:36,120
Nonsense!

168
00:09:36,639 --> 00:09:37,639
You're slandering!

169
00:09:39,039 --> 00:09:40,840
What type of person

170
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:41,919
made your heart race last night?

171
00:09:42,679 --> 00:09:44,159
If any man married you,

172
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:46,200
he'd be eating porridge every day,

173
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:48,039
living on scraps.

174
00:09:49,120 --> 00:09:51,120
(You'd better worry about
the mad Ling Xiao.)

175
00:09:57,159 --> 00:09:58,440
What game are you playing now?

176
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:00,840
I'm having a high fever,

177
00:10:01,639 --> 00:10:02,720
and it hurts so much!

178
00:10:03,399 --> 00:10:04,919
Don't you know
that I'm a skilled physician?

179
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:07,080
Let me see your hand.

180
00:10:08,679 --> 00:10:10,240
If you lie to me again,

181
00:10:10,879 --> 00:10:12,279
I'll have you confined to the palace

182
00:10:13,279 --> 00:10:14,799
to reflect on what you've done.

183
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:17,639
So cold...

184
00:10:18,399 --> 00:10:19,080
So cold...

185
00:10:21,159 --> 00:10:22,000
So cold...

186
00:10:22,559 --> 00:10:23,679
I'm so cold...

187
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,039
The weather is still warm.

188
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:28,120
How did you catch such a bad cold?

189
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:30,840
What kind of care
have you been giving His Majesty?

190
00:10:31,039 --> 00:10:31,799
I wouldn't dare ignore this.

191
00:10:32,159 --> 00:10:33,919
I've been by His Majesty's side
every moment.

192
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:38,159
Perhaps His Majesty
has indeed been struck by some wind.

193
00:10:39,399 --> 00:10:41,440
Mo Shuo, don't blame him.

194
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:43,600
My body is weak.

195
00:10:44,159 --> 00:10:45,519
I feel so terrible.

196
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:46,799
I feel awful.

197
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:47,639
Your Majesty,

198
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,200
take a rest for now.

199
00:10:52,159 --> 00:10:52,759
Sheng,

200
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:53,960
you take good care of His Majesty.

201
00:10:54,159 --> 00:10:54,960
I'm going to prepare the remedy.

202
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:55,919
Understood.

203
00:11:07,399 --> 00:11:09,399
(Your Majesty,
your health is paramount,)

204
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:11,200
(You'll catch a cold.)

205
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:13,600
(Mo Shuo is skilled in medicine.)

206
00:11:14,039 --> 00:11:15,600
(He won't be fooled so easily.)

207
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:17,240
(Come on, keep going!)

208
00:11:17,440 --> 00:11:18,720
(More water... on me!)

209
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:20,240
(Water! Hurry!)

210
00:11:20,639 --> 00:11:21,799
(Even the gods themselves)

211
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:24,000
(cannot compare to
Your Majesty's divine status!)

212
00:11:24,639 --> 00:11:26,799
(Is it really important for you to
go to the Qixi Festival?)

213
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:28,480
(It is to me.)

214
00:11:28,879 --> 00:11:30,120
(Because I made a promise to someone.)

215
00:11:30,559 --> 00:11:31,840
(Hurry! Keep going!)

216
00:11:32,279 --> 00:11:32,919
(More!)

217
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:35,559
Your Majesty,

218
00:11:36,039 --> 00:11:37,720
why would you go to such lengths?

219
00:11:38,159 --> 00:11:39,759
Who could possibly deserve this
from you?

220
00:11:40,679 --> 00:11:42,279
Who is out there?

221
00:11:42,879 --> 00:11:44,200
I must go find her.

222
00:11:44,559 --> 00:11:45,480
I promised her.

223
00:11:51,799 --> 00:11:52,519
So pretty!

224
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:53,080
Isn't it?

225
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:54,080
I want another one later.

226
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:54,840
Sure.

227
00:11:55,559 --> 00:11:57,519
Why is everyone wearing masks?

228
00:11:58,440 --> 00:12:00,159
They say that on Qixi Festival,

229
00:12:00,519 --> 00:12:02,120
even if you can't see
each other's faces,

230
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:05,000
the gods will bring your fated one

231
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:06,200
to your side.

232
00:12:07,279 --> 00:12:07,960
Really?

233
00:12:08,919 --> 00:12:10,279
Then, with my mask,

234
00:12:10,519 --> 00:12:12,519
only the gods will accept me?

235
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:14,840
My Lady,

236
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:17,320
are you still going around
in that pig-head mask?

237
00:12:17,519 --> 00:12:18,840
People have been staring at us
the whole way.

238
00:12:19,279 --> 00:12:20,480
Come on!

239
00:12:20,759 --> 00:12:21,279
Besides,

240
00:12:21,799 --> 00:12:23,200
no sneaking drinks today.

241
00:12:23,519 --> 00:12:25,159
I like it. Don't judge me!

242
00:12:25,679 --> 00:12:26,679
If I catch you,

243
00:12:26,879 --> 00:12:28,279
I'll cut off your allowance.

244
00:12:29,759 --> 00:12:30,919
You cheapskate!

245
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:34,480
I'm done being your pig-headed maid.

246
00:12:35,120 --> 00:12:36,080
I'm going out to look around.

247
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:38,799
I still have dagger stalls to browse.

248
00:12:39,519 --> 00:12:40,799
Off you go.

249
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:41,960
I know

250
00:12:41,960 --> 00:12:43,919
you're going to meet your lover.

251
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:45,120
That's not true!

252
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:46,480
I'm off.

253
00:12:49,799 --> 00:12:50,320
See you.

254
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:09,120
Sorry,

255
00:13:09,679 --> 00:13:10,600
I'm late.
